    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a museum-quality 2008 Porsche 911 Carrera S (997.1) finished in Basalt Black Metallic. This specimen features the M97.01 3.8L flat-six engine, delivering 355 hp with a perfectly linear torque curve. Meticulously maintained, the G97 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp, short-throw engagement. The chassis is equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM), featuring a 10mm lower ride height and recalibrated damping for superior lateral stability. Recent mechanical overhaul includes a documented IMS bearing retrofit and a full borescope inspection confirming zero cylinder wall scoring. The braking system retains its original bite with four-piston aluminum monobloc calipers and ventilated cross-drilled rotors. Zero cosmetic or mechanical flaws; this is a turn-key collector-grade vehicle.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
