    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive excellence, this vehicle is in showroom-ready, mint condition. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with professional ceramic coating, showing absolutely no rock chips, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains a pristine time capsule; the premium leather seats are supple with zero bolster wear, and the original factory scent remains. Every surface, from the brushed aluminum accents to the high-definition displays, is flawless and functions as if it just rolled off the assembly line. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been strictly garage-kept and maintained exclusively at certified dealerships. We have a complete binder of meticulous service records, including a recent comprehensive inspection and full fluid flush. It rides on a fresh set of high-performance tires and comes complete with both original keys, all factory manuals, and the original window sticker. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection, this is a rare opportunity to own a flawless specimen.",
      "price": 48500.0,
